Hysteria:

"Acknowledged commander. Hysteria out."

Hysteria had slowly been tapping out the comands in order to reroute as much 
of the reserve power as possible. In order for this to succeed she'd have to 
find a way to stabalize the shields. At most they'd last a few seconds 
before completely failing or closing the section. It was worth a shot.

CF COMP: Reroute complete. Ten seconds until shield is inoperative inenemy 
'bots' vicinity.

Hysteria opened a comm to the Alliance 'bots inside the shields:

"Attention Alliance 'bots, once the shields are dropped you will have 
aproximately ten senconds until they are reactivated. Tech 'bot out."

Hysteria tapped out the final command and waited as the shields in front of 
the Alliance 'bots dropped, leaving that one section vulnerable as the rest 
fluctuated dangerously.
